            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《機動戰士高達 SEED FREEDOM》 劇場版終於也在香港 Netflix 播放了，Bandai 也在近這兩個月內也相繼推出了《SEED FREEDOM》的兩部主角機體模型，HGCE 突擊自由高達極，以及 HGCE 無限正義高達二型，這兩部高人氣機體模型方面表現如何呢？先要説説小編近日比較忙，加上面對著這兩部大熱人氣機體模型，不作一些塗裝及上水貼等工序實在不行，今次的評測報告的確是遲來了，請不要見怪啊！既然是遲了，那就連最近的 HGCE 無限正義高達二型製作好了，一起報告吧。</p><p><a title="_DSC0217" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700865/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700865_6214accbb9_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0217" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC0216" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700895/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700895_ec6f60d57e_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0216" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>HGCE 無限正義高達二型</h2><p>説實在的，小編是比較喜愛正義高達，多過自由高達，特別是在今次《機動戰士高達 SEED FREEDOM》劇場版中的表現，阿斯蘭及無限正義高達二式非常亮眼，特別是無限正義高達二式登場時非常驚艷，無限正義在魔蟹外殼中破殼而出，這樣的設定已令很多模型高手改裝模型，以還原這樣的情節。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9604-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9604-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9604-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>無限正義二式看來與原版差異不大，但仔細比較會發現很多改良之處。關節的銀色關節採用了光澤銀製作，不是平時一般的銀色，看起來更亮眼。胸口取消了綠色輪廓線，整體輪廓更加修長纖細。肩甲尺寸更大。頭部保留了長臉尖下巴的特徵，但面頰輪廓更直線化。頭部側面火神炮移至頭頂，但取消了分色。胸口出氣口實現了分色，複合盾牌的黃色部分也採用了分件分色。</p><p><a title="_DSC0227" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909258671/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909258671_e5e78ec285_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0227" width="689" height="1024" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0241" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909504818/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909504818_d0ca964e8c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0241" width="1024" height="758" /></a></p><p>骨架方面採用了新型 SEED 系列的設計，整體可動性出色。腰部採用三段式結構，彎腰幅度優秀。肩部可動範圍大，手臂前伸和平抬都很到位。膝關節屈膝幅度出色，小腿新增了左右擺動關節，可以擺出更生動的踢姿勢。</p><p><a title="_DSC0247" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909603049/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909603049_f609cf70e5_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0247" width="1024" height="697" /></a></p><p>除了原有的光束步槍、複合盾牌等武裝外，二式最大的特色是頭頂可展開巨大光束軍刀。不過模型中這個部件比例偏短小，效果大打折扣，以模型的頭部光束軍刀長度根本很難會刺中敵機吧？</p><p><a title="_DSC0162" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909564149/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909564149_46396f7830_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0162" width="1024" height="697" /></a></p><p>揹包可變形為支援機，四把光束刀插上後，還原劇中造型，不過外觀亦非常似星戰的 X-Wing 戰機。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0229-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0229-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0229.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><a title="_DSC0266" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909504813/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909504813_4b62faa278_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0266" width="1024" height="814" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0232" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909603054/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909603054_ca7f4e654a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0232" width="1024" height="664" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC0252" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909258641/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909258641_3b8e18d2b1_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0252" width="1024" height="821" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />
小編極為期待 Bandai 宣佈之後會推出的 HG 1/144 魔蟹 (SEED FREEDOM Ver.)，不知道會是如何設定正義高達塞在魔蟹的體內呢？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/452806678_1066628288-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/452806678_1066628288-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/452806678_1066628288.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>模型名稱：HGCE 無限正義高達二型<br />
參考售價：2,800 日圓（不含稅）<br />
查詢：瑞華行</p><h2>HGCE 突擊自由高達極</h2><p>突擊自由高達極 (之後簡稱突自極)，與原版突擊自由極為相似，部份位置有點改良，整體造型更帶點力量感覺，肩部位置採用了新規設計，其中灰色部份肩甲更帶來點爭議。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255340" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9430-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9430-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9430-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255341" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9438-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9438-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9438-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255342" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9477-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9477-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9477-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>當然最大亮點就是全新設計的揹包自豪防衞者 PROUD DEFENDER，翅膀採用內外雙層葉片結構，展開後可見內部金色葉片，而今次的金色算是比以前一般的模型金色已來得好了，素組派可能會接受到，高點要求的玩家當然就是，自己噴過吧 (小編也是自行噴塗)。雖然有粉紅色的 3D 貼紙在縫隙點綴一下，不過亦可能由於是 HG 級模型的關係，小編總感覺這個揹包實在太白淨了，製作時唯有盡量加多點水貼，才可以接受到。</p><p><a title="_DSC0200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909504843/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909504843_e94f5a1be5_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0200" width="1024" height="933" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0201" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909603074/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909603074_d563754309_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0201" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC0203" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700880/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700880_0c1b4c13bd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0203" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0120" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53908364537/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53908364537_3196c703fb_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0120" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>另一亮點就是新武器實體武士刀「布都御魂」，在黑色的同一零件上，運用了 2 種表面處理來達到質感差異；分色方面也算是做得不錯，唯有在刀柄末端的小小金色部份就需要自己塗裝了。</p><p><a title="_DSC0198" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700890/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700890_1d8a961ecc_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0198" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>主體部份採用了 SEED 系列最新的關節設計，可動性方面的確是有提升，肩部改為關節組設計，軀幹關節有點似飛昇自由，腰部和腿部關節也有改良。</p><p><a title="_DSC0168" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53908364517/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53908364517_f39353814a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0168" width="1024" height="818" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0175" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700930/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700930_eec15fe4d7_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0175" width="1024" height="904" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0185" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909603099/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909603099_b73f39041a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0185" width="1024" height="833" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0191" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909258721/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909258721_a4b92b324f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0191" width="1024" height="1013" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0194" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53908364487/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53908364487_79488eeac6_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0194" width="1024" height="998" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0196" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700910/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700910_ce161fb141_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0196" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0197" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909504863/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909504863_ac2df976a0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0197" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>模型名稱：HGCE 突擊自由高達極<br />
參考售價：2,600 日圓（不含稅）<br />
查詢：瑞華行</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/hgcefreedomjusticeii/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【評測】HGCE 突擊自由高達極　HGCE 無限正義高達二型</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
