        <item>
            <title>「微信保險」詐騙電話 Cut 線會打來問原因　連登網民分享對付騙徒新招</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wechat-scam</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 08:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[資訊保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[wechat]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信保險]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[詐騙電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[騙案]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1255279</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">最近不少人都有收到「微信保險」的詐騙電話或短訊，聲稱其開通的微信資金安全保險已經到期，按每月 $2000 收費三年總共需扣費 $72000。網上討論區同樣有網友收到了「微信保險」的詐騙電話，雖未有受騙但抱怨被詐騙電話騷擾，而且騙徒的態度極不友善。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255294 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2170-1-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2170-1-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2170-1.jpg 806w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3758300/page/2">LIHKG</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">網友抱怨騙徒用幾個不同的電話不斷向他致電，即使接聽後立即掛斷電話騙徒也會馬上回電，令他十分困擾。他表示騙徒會要求他講普通話，即使向對方辱罵亦無動於衷。不少網民均表示同樣收到了類似的來電和短訊並分享自己的經歷，表示「cut 完線即刻再打嚟問我做乜 cut 佢線」、「X 我唔講普通話」、「上次 X 完佢佢用廿幾個唔同號碼打嚟」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255295 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2172-1-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2172-1-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2172-1.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1255296" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2173-1-694x415.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="415" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2173-1-694x415.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2173-1.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3758300/page/2">LIHKG</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">有網民就分享了不會再被騙徒騷擾的方法，指只需要用純正的普通話辱罵他們便不會再打來，或向騙徒表示沒有安裝任何中國大陸的應用程式後，騙徒就會自動掛斷電話。有網民以 $2000 太少不在乎來回應騙徒後，更獲騙徒祝他身體健康。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255298 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2176-1-428x580.jpg" alt="" width="428" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2176-1-428x580.jpg 428w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2176-1.jpg 664w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 428px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255297 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2175-1-694x286.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="286" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2175-1-694x286.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2175-1.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1255299 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2177-1-e1723099192870-626x580.jpg" alt="" width="626" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2177-1-e1723099192870-626x580.jpg 626w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2177-1-e1723099192870-971x900.jpg 971w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2177-1-e1723099192870.jpg 1169w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 626px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3758300/page/2">LIHKG</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3758300/page/2">LIHKG</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/wellcome-scam/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SMS 騙案假扮惠康積分換領網站　加 $4.7 換領氣炸鍋呃信用卡資料</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/03/apple-chinascam/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國詐騙集團假 iPhone 換真機     Apple 十年被騙超過 9600 萬港元</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/03/hkdoublescam/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">警方接獲 6 宗網上「二次詐騙」案，苦主被騙後再損失多一次「律師費」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/">「微信保險」詐騙電話 Cut 線會打來問原因　連登網民分享對付騙徒新招</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
