        <item>
            <title>DJI 無人機幫珠穆朗瑪峯清垃圾，運送物資節省人力更安全高效</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/nepal-plan-to-use-dji-drones-to-help-clean-up-everest-region-mountain/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nepal-plan-to-use-dji-drones-to-help-clean-up-everest-region-mountain</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/nepal-plan-to-use-dji-drones-to-help-clean-up-everest-region-mountain/life-tech/drone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:00:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅遊]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[環保]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[航拍]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[dji]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[DJI FlyCart 30]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[無人機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1255133</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">尼泊爾正計劃部署 DJI 無人機來取代雪巴人在珠穆朗瑪峯地區搬運物資和清理廢物，開創高海拔物流領域的先河。這個決定將能大大減低傳統上由人類進行搬運的危險任務所帶來的風險。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255144 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/58b0607eb8b24521bcea-694x363.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/58b0607eb8b24521bcea-694x363.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/58b0607eb8b24521bcea.jpeg 1252w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/08/07/dji-drones-nepal-moutain-everest/">Gizmochina</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255146 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/flycartcargo-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/flycartcargo-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/flycartcargo.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://enterprise.dronenerds.com/commercial-drone-platforms/dji-flycart-30/">Drone Nerds Enterprise</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">傳統上雪巴人負責在高山運送氧氣瓶、帳篷、食物等物資和清理垃圾，每季需要穿越非常危險的冰瀑 30 多次，單單是 1953-2023 年就有近 50 人在冰瀑上喪生。無人機的工作相信會由 DJI 的 FlyCart 30 來執行，最大負重為 30 KG 且支援 6000 米最高飛行海拔高度，能承受 -20°C &#8211; 45°C 的工作環境溫度和每秒 12 米的最大抗風速度。前期測試中，DJI 無人機每小時可運送 234 公斤垃圾，同樣重量需用上 14 名搬運工和 6 小時才能完成。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_99991"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Hhp11I-vGHA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">有人指無人機將會奪去了雪巴人的工作，但官員和登山者一致認為無人機將能有效改善安全和環境條件，而無人機的操作亦會交由雪巴人操作。由於人口過度擁擠和氣候變化，珠穆朗瑪峯地區面臨越來越大的挑戰，導致廢棄物顯著累積。無人機預計將在這個脆弱生態系統中發揮關鍵作用。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/08/07/dji-drones-nepal-moutain-everest/">Gizmochina</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/01/11/dji-flycart-30-long-range-high-payload-design-unveiled/">Gizmochina</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/02/dji-neo-photo-leaked/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">DJI Neo 小巧航拍機，真機照網上流傳</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/31/dji-neo-drone-specs-price-leak/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全新航拍機試飛影片外洩，袋裝 DJI Neo 零售價格提前曝光</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/dji-x-hasselblad/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">DJI | Hasselblad 哈蘇概念店　於澳門新濠影滙正式開業</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/nepal-plan-to-use-dji-drones-to-help-clean-up-everest-region-mountain/life-tech/drone/">DJI 無人機幫珠穆朗瑪峯清垃圾，運送物資節省人力更安全高效</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
